@startuml
title ATM Withdrawal State Diagram

state "Display Options" as DisplayOptions
state "User Selection" as UserSelection
state "Custom Amount" as CustomAmount
state "Transaction Verification" as TransactionVerification
state "Re-Enter Amount" as ReEnterAmount
state "Dispense Cash" as DispenseCash
state "Insufficient Funds" as InsufficientFunds
state "End Session" as EndSession

DisplayOptions : do / Show available options
UserSelection : entry / User selects an option
UserSelection : do / Validate user selection
UserSelection : exit / Amount set

CustomAmount : entry / No option selected
CustomAmount : do / Prompt user to enter custom amount
CustomAmount : exit / Custom amount entered

TransactionVerification : entry / Amount verified
TransactionVerification : do / Check account balance
TransactionVerification : exit / Transaction accepted or rejected

ReEnterAmount : entry / Transaction rejected
ReEnterAmount : do / Prompt user to re-enter amount
ReEnterAmount : exit / Re-entered amount

DispenseCash : entry / Amount verified and sufficient funds available
DispenseCash : do / Dispense cash and return change
DispenseCash : exit / Cash dispensed

InsufficientFunds : entry / Insufficient funds
InsufficientFunds : do / Notify user of insufficient funds
InsufficientFunds : exit / End session

EndSession : entry / Transaction completed
EndSession : do / End the ATM session
EndSession : exit / [*]

DisplayOptions --> UserSelection
UserSelection --> CustomAmount
CustomAmount --> TransactionVerification
TransactionVerification --> ReEnterAmount
ReEnterAmount --> TransactionVerification
TransactionVerification --> DispenseCash
TransactionVerification --> InsufficientFunds

InsufficientFunds --> EndSession
DispenseCash --> EndSession
@enduml
